<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<title>Embedding SVG Into HTML Pages</title>
</head>
<body>

<!-- thanks to code lab, https://www.tutorialrepublic.com/html-tutorial/html5-svg.php -->
<!-- for 1) full screen & ZOOMABLE svg go: height:auto + width:101% + remove overflow:hidden .. 2) centered/contained svg go: height:101vh + width:101% + overflow:hidden -->
<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" viewBox="0 0 239.04 312" style="height:auto !important;width:101% !important;margin: -10px !important;overflow: hidde !important;background-color: #121212 !important;text-align:center !important;display:block !important;">
  <g>
    <rect width="239.04" height="312" fill="#fffef5" />
  </g>
  <image width="996" height="930" transform="translate(0 88.8) scale(0.24)" xlink:href="data:image/png;base64,"/>
  <image width="193" height="88" transform="translate(188.88 270.72) scale(0.24)" xlink:href="data:image/png;base64,"/>
</svg>

</body>
</html>
